<dl id="n40057c"> <dt class="nbunit"><a name="n40" href="#n40057c">N40 (VI.B.28B)</a>:  <a href="../../FF/fnbs/n40all.htm#n40057c"> 57(c)</a></dt> <dd> <blockquote> domovoy / colours</blockquote> <dd class="well"> <blockquote class="sources">In Russia the <i>domovoi</i> (house spirit) is an important personage in folk-belief; he may object to certain kinds of animals, or to certain colours in cattle; and must, generally speaking, be propitiated and cared for. <small> &ldquo;DEMONOLOGY&rdquo; <a name="EBDY" href="../../FF/fdra/fdex.htm#EBDY"><cite title="source">Encyclopaedia Britannica</cite></a>, 11th edit. (1911) 7</small></blockquote> </dd></dl>
